etime.\n            ",[1904,2249],"\n              Turacos Tours is a locally owned Rwandan tour company passionate about sharing the incredible beauty of our country. We specialize in wildlife safaris, gorilla tracking, and cultural immersions. Our expert local guides bring Rwanda&lsquo;s stories, landscapes, and wildlife to life — creating memories that last a lifetime.\n            ",[1904,2249],"\n              Turacos Tours is a locally owned Rwandan tour company passionate about sharing the incredible beauty of our country. We specialize in wildlife safaris, gorilla tracking, and cultural immersions. Our expert local guides bring Rwanda&#39;s stories, landscapes, and wildlife to life — creating memories that last a lifetime.\n            ",[1904,2249],"\n              Turacos Tours is a locally owned Rwandan tour company passionate about sharing the incredible beauty of our country. We specialize in wildlife safaris, gorilla tracking, and cultural immersions. Our expert local guides bring Rwanda&rsquo;s stories, landscapes, and wildlife to life — creating memories that last a lifetime.\n            ",[4697,4820],"\n                &quot;We don't just guide you through Rwanda; we open the heart of the Heart of Africa for you.\"\n              ",[4697,4820],"\n                &ldquo;We don't just guide you through Rwanda; we open the heart of the Heart of Africa for you.\"\n              ",[4697,4820],"\n                &#34;We don't just guide you through Rwanda; we open the heart of the Heart of Africa for you.\"\n              ",[4697,4820],"\n                &rdquo;We don't just guide you through Rwanda; we open the heart of the Heart of Africa for you.\"\n              ",[4697,4820],"\n                \"We don&apos;t just guide you through Rwanda; we open the heart of the Heart of Africa for you.\"\n              ",[4697,4820],"\n                \"We don&lsquo;t just guide you through Rwanda; we open the heart of the Heart of Africa for you.\"\n            